  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091227" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">蜗杆滚珠传动装置，本发明是属机械工程，本发明是提高蜗杆传动装置的效率和扩大蜗杆传动装置的使用领域，蜗杆滚珠传动装置的特征是由蜗杆、滚珠、滚珠导轨和滚珠回路所组成。蜗杆滚珠传动装置体积小，结构紧凑，传动效率高，角速比大，运输平稳，无噪声，适用于机械设备的增速和减速传动，定级和变级传动以及高速传动。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091227" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The patent refers to the field of 'gearing'.It is characterized by that it is made up of the worm, the balls, the guide rack and the return passage for the balls. It offers the merits of small volume, compact structure, high transmission efficiency, high angular velocity ratio, steady running, no noise. It is suitable to be used in acceleration and deceleration transmission, fixed stage and variable stage transmission as well as high speed transmission for the machinery equipment.</p>
  </abstract>
